question: What drugs target NDUFA6?
cypher:
MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('NDUFA6')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('NDUFA6'))
RETURN
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('IGF1R'))
RETURN
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('PORCN')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('PORCN'))
RETURN
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('ALK')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('ALK'))
RETURN
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('NDUFA1')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('NDUFA1'))
RETURN
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('RET')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('RET'))
RETURN
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50
